1945;;Crime, Inc.;;American;;Lew Landers;;Leo Carrillo, Tom Neal;;thriller;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Crime,_Inc._(1945_film);;The film, based on a story by former crime reporter Martin Mooney, is about a newspaper journalist who faces prison time because he refuses to name his sources. To complicate matters more, the reporter falls in love with the sister of one of the racketeers he's trying to take down.